commenter.name: maxxxtakeover
commenter.bio: I’ve started playing kaizo Mario but sometimes I stream myself playing guitar

message.body: @MaxxxTakeOver Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input).
